{"tid":1171720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反對《逃犯條例》修訂，向美國白宮遞交聯署","createTime":"2019-05-26T02:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T01:49:49.000Z","uid":185066,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"569969af12bc9202916ded119a6f788c8f2b2765","tid":1171720,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"一齊推埋白宮出聲啦 無論你地覺得有冇用 一人一簽名都可以積少成多 如果你地有心關注香港既未來 就唔好怕用一分鐘時間入去簽一簽個名<br />\n<br />\n【聯署】<br />\n*反對《逃犯條例》修訂，向美國白宮遞交聯署*，如人數達10萬，白宮就必須回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e19f4cb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n請聯署及廣傳🙏🏻"},{"pid":"561cae99d5f0f5f7f41512b43318ec7968516e6b","tid":1171720,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"我會推曬所有有關聯署嘅post<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家認真看待 多一個簽名 多一分力量 <br />\n無論覺得有無用都好 做咗先<br />\nshare曬俾所有朋友 親人 中同大同同事<br />\n甚至外國朋友 今朝到依家已經多咗5000幾份聯署<br />\n仲差6萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間就只得半個月"},{"pid":"421cc6a9897d8f7d44a77c7f686253d6aef19423","tid":1171720,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466930f077ab73fc289b2adca6225d8e62ac7498","tid":1171720,"uid":185066,